Contains classes-controllers for administrator's actions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdministratorAction
    Provides basic operation(action) for administrator.
    HorseRaceEditAction
    Process input data from administrator about horseRaces for some race.
    HorseRaceResultEditAction
    Process input data from administrator about horseRaces for some race.
    HorseRaceResultSaveAction
    Process input data from administrator about horseRaces for save changes.
    RaceDeleteAction
    Process input data from administrator about race for delete this race.
    RaceEditAction
    Forwarding administrator to page for editing races.
    RaceListAction
    Forming list of future and passed races for show to administrator.
    RaceSaveAction
    Processing input data from administrator for save new race.
